<h2>How to use this registry</h2>
<p>When building any feature for XP/XB/Voice/Beeper/SMS/Mail/Pane/Wrapper/MCP go-to-market:</p>
<p>1. **Pre-build:** scan the relevant domain section, list every complaint that touches the feature.</p>
