<p>3. **Test:** for each complaint in the relevant domain, define a verification step and run it.</p>
<p>4. **Ship:** only when ALL relevant complaints have a green verification trace.</p>
<p>5. **Update:** when a new complaint surfaces, append here AND to a feedback file.</p>
